1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:31,530 --> 00:01:36,020
[A Lonely Hero's Journey]

3
00:01:36,330 --> 00:01:38,780
[Episode 25]

4
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:41,479
This was found at Huang Xinzhai's place.

5
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:44,930
I didn't pay attention last time.

6
00:01:45,050 --> 00:01:47,810
Later, the more I look at it, the more it looks like a person.

7
00:01:47,810 --> 00:01:50,370
The butler of Gu Yizhong.

8
00:01:50,509 --> 00:01:52,370
His name is something like Fu Gui.

9
00:02:00,470 --> 00:02:02,370
Why did Huang Xinzhai

10
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,880
draw a portrait of Fu Gui?

11
00:02:04,390 --> 00:02:07,030
I don't think Huang Xinzhai is capable of that.

12
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:09,710
It's the brushwork of Painter Li from the Fourth Branch,

13
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:10,910
who specializes in painting portraits of suspects.

14
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:13,030
It's the portrait of the person who rented the house

15
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:15,690
and who masterminded the digging of the tunnel.

16
00:02:17,290 --> 00:02:18,750
Huang Xinzhai

17
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,490
didn't do anything good when he was alive.

18
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:24,210
But he did us a big favor after he died.

19
00:02:24,990 --> 00:02:25,710
Sir,

20
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:27,680
once we arrest Fu Gui,

21
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:30,000
Gu Yizhong will show his true colors.

22
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:37,990
Mr. Gu,

23
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:41,990
are you going out?

24
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,270
I have an appointment with an undercover agent

25
00:02:43,270 --> 00:02:44,510
at the tea house.

26
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:45,960
I'm afraid

27
00:02:46,490 --> 00:02:49,020
you're going to break the appointment today.

28
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:56,510
[Explore the secluded world]

29
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:54,960
Please go in.

30
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:56,670
Mr. Kondo is waiting inside.

31
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:06,990
Sir.

32
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:10,580
Mr. Iwai said you want to see me for some urgent matter.

33
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,930
I like this garden very much.

34
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,470
This is

35
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:19,079
a typical Suzhou landscape

36
00:03:19,510 --> 00:03:22,430
with pavilions and winding paths leading to a secluded place.

37
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:24,090
I didn't expect that Mr. Kondo

38
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,950
loves gardens of Suzhou so much.

39
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:29,010
Mr. Kondo,

40
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:31,060
what can I do for you?

41
00:03:31,230 --> 00:03:32,760
Please feel free to tell me.

42
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:37,120
The Sino-Japanese Cultural Association in Suzhou,

43
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:39,930
including food and architecture,

44
00:03:40,350 --> 00:03:42,680
which are also part of cultural exchange,

45
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,070
trains and educates Chinese children

46
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:46,990
and Japanese children, letting them grow up together.

47
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:48,990
I'm going to elect you

48
00:03:49,130 --> 00:03:52,930
as President of the Sino-Japanese Cultural Association in Suzhou.

49
00:03:57,060 --> 00:03:57,730
Sir,

50
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:01,040
I'm afraid that I'm not qualified for it.

51
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:02,680
Mr. Kondo.

52
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,700
I'm still inexperienced.

53
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,500
In No. 90 Agent Station,

54
00:04:06,790 --> 00:04:08,230
there's Director Zhou in the senior level

55
00:04:08,230 --> 00:04:10,670
and directors of various departments in the lower level.

56
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:12,490
I'm just an ordinary agent.

57
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:14,540
It would be hardly convincing.

58
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:17,070
Are you worried that Zhou Zhifei won't agree?

59
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:26,970
To be honest, I don't like Mr. Zhou.

60
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,770
He doesn't do things for the peace movement.

61
00:04:29,770 --> 00:04:31,570
He only does things for himself.

62
00:04:31,910 --> 00:04:33,710
He won't have future prospects.

63
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:37,040
You once studied abroad in the U.S.

64
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:40,210
Your educational background, knowledge, and experience

65
00:04:40,210 --> 00:04:42,690
are totally different from Zhou Zhifei.

66
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:46,520
Sir, I'm flattered.

67
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:48,409
Don't worry.

68
00:04:48,990 --> 00:04:50,830
You will be a competent president.

69
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:52,030
As long as you work hard,

70
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:55,590
you'll also be the Director of the agent station sooner or later.

71
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:58,120
Please accept the appointment as president.

72
00:05:00,030 --> 00:05:01,040
Sino-Japanese Cultural Association?

73
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,770
Yes.

74
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,810
Sino-Japanese Cultural Association.

75
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:06,030
I heard Wang Zemin say before

76
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:09,070
that the Japanese wanted to found this association.

77
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:09,990
They wanted to govern the cultural,

78
00:05:09,990 --> 00:05:12,850
industrial, and commercial industries of Suzhou.

79
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:16,550
But they shouldn't ask Gu Yizhong

80
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:18,010
to lead the association.

81
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,840
His resume doesn't qualify him for the work.

82
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,050
Every one of us in the station

83
00:05:21,050 --> 00:05:22,840
is more qualified than he is.

84
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,640
Is it about experience and qualification?

85
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:27,910
Have you ever gone overseas?

86
00:05:27,910 --> 00:05:29,590
No, I never live on the sea.

87
00:05:36,790 --> 00:05:38,070
I mean,

88
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:40,500
have you ever studied abroad

89
00:05:40,659 --> 00:05:42,450
like Gu Yizhong did?

90
00:05:42,909 --> 00:05:45,510
He speaks English, knows architecture well,

91
00:05:45,530 --> 00:05:46,450
and can draw.

92
00:05:46,930 --> 00:05:48,530
How can you compare with him?

93
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,659
I know.

94
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,470
Jiping, you've been

95
00:05:52,470 --> 00:05:54,900
eyeing the position of Vice Director, right?

96
00:05:54,900 --> 00:05:55,750
Don't worry.

97
00:05:55,780 --> 00:05:57,180
When the timing is right,

98
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:58,510
I'll speak for you.

99
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:01,310
I'm just afraid that the Japanese

100
00:06:01,350 --> 00:06:02,730
have their own ideas.

101
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:06,830
Director, you have the final say

102
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:09,360
on the personnel matters of No. 90.

103
00:06:12,230 --> 00:06:13,960
Where is Fu Gui now?

104
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,690
He's in Dingjue Temple.

105
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:19,840
How about this?

106
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,220
Take some men

107
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:24,330
and go over there to arrest Fu Gui.

108
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:24,950
Okay.

109
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:27,190
We must force Gu Yizhong to take action.

110
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:27,790
Okay.

111
00:06:30,610 --> 00:06:31,690
I'm good.

112
00:06:32,180 --> 00:06:32,670
You…

113
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:35,090
You should go and do your work.

114
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,200
He's quite good at this.

115
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:55,550
[Buddhism]

116
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,190
Here. It's here.

117
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:01,550
Come.

118
00:07:10,150 --> 00:07:11,010
Where is Fu Gui?

119
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,030
He is in the main hall.

120
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:23,830
Hurry up! Something went wrong!

121
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:24,910
Something went wrong!

122
00:07:24,910 --> 00:07:26,170
Something went wrong!

123
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:33,120
Section Chief Xie, it's you again.

124
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,750
You're here to kowtow to Master Gu again?

125
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:36,630
I'm here

126
00:07:37,030 --> 00:07:38,570
to take you back to No. 90.

127
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:39,390
Go!

128
00:07:39,470 --> 00:07:40,870
Who are you to arrest her?

129
00:07:41,130 --> 00:07:42,330
Do you know who she is?

130
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:45,340
A CBIS agent from Chongqing.

131
00:07:53,820 --> 00:07:54,890
Section Chief Xie.

132
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,810
You arrested another woman?

133
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:00,310
The women's prison is full.

134
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,170
Full?

135
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:04,490
If it's full, then send her to your place.

136
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:05,370
Sure.

137
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:08,430
Tie her up on the electric chair.

138
00:08:16,110 --> 00:08:17,440
Don't you dare not tell!

139
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,190
Do you tell us or not?

140
00:08:22,970 --> 00:08:23,830
Where is Haimo?

141
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:26,970
I'm asking you where Haimo is.

142
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:32,780
She knows nothing.

143
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:35,120
She has nothing to do with our business.

144
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,380
Why did you arrest her?

145
00:08:37,190 --> 00:08:39,000
You're obviously framing her.

146
00:08:47,630 --> 00:08:50,510
You have no manners.

147
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:52,470
Right.

148
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:54,830
Someone might have framed her.

149
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:56,360
That's why we need Miss Haimo

150
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,250
to come to No. 90

151
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:59,550
to assist in the investigation.

152
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:01,890
Is there a problem?

153
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:11,990
Mr. Kondo.

154
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:15,700
[Profile]

155
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:18,180
Do you know someone named Haimo?

156
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:24,390
Yes, I do.

157
00:09:26,330 --> 00:09:27,330
Is it this person?

158
00:09:30,970 --> 00:09:34,420
[Name: Zhang Haimo] [Address: Currently residing in Gu's Garden]

159
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,510
She came from Chongqing

160
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:37,410
and is a member of the CBIS.

161
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,010
Mr. Kondo.

162
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:42,810
She's not from Chongqing.

163
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:44,310
Nor is she a member of the CBIS.

164
00:09:44,310 --> 00:09:46,000
We've investigated it thoroughly.

165
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,210
Zhang Haimo

166
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,370
is a member of the CBIS from Chongqing.

167
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:51,510
She was the subordinate of Ou Xinping,

168
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:53,440
who was executed by me personally.

169
00:10:02,250 --> 00:10:04,710
Mr. Kondo, this is a misunderstanding. She…

170
00:10:08,190 --> 00:10:09,000
She's not…

171
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:10,610
She's not Haimo.

172
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,470
Then who is she?

173
00:10:13,170 --> 00:10:13,860
Gu Yizhong.

174
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,620
Think carefully before you talk.

175
00:10:26,990 --> 00:10:28,830
Your superior, Director Ou,

176
00:10:29,950 --> 00:10:32,030
had also sat on the seat

177
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:34,150
that you're sitting on now.

178
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:37,240
She has confessed everything she should confess.

179
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:38,950
If you're sensible,

180
00:10:40,770 --> 00:10:42,230
just confess everything.

181
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,220
If the power is on,

182
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:50,070
your hands

183
00:10:50,910 --> 00:10:51,990
will be burnt.

184
00:10:55,190 --> 00:10:56,470
She is my fiancée.

185
00:11:13,390 --> 00:11:15,320
My late father and Haimo's father,

186
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:16,990
Mr. Zhang Yuquan,

187
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:19,240
made an engagement 15 years ago

188
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:21,270
and we'll get married.

189
00:11:23,710 --> 00:11:26,190
She's just a lady performer of storytelling accompanied by string instruments.

190
00:11:26,190 --> 00:11:27,850
She's by no means a CBIS agent.

191
00:11:29,870 --> 00:11:30,790
Really?

192
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:32,500
I tell nothing but the truth.

193
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:35,310
You're engaged and living in the same room.

194
00:11:35,590 --> 00:11:37,130
Why aren't you married?

195
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:39,780
I don't think people from Suzhou do this.

196
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:48,190
Sir.

197
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:51,210
I was born and raised in Suzhou,

198
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:53,330
and I've never heard of it.

199
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:55,810
But my intelligence shows

200
00:11:56,190 --> 00:11:58,590
that Zhang Haimo and Ou Xinping

201
00:11:59,070 --> 00:12:02,000
traveled from Hong Kong to Shanghai by British ship,

202
00:12:02,340 --> 00:12:05,120
then came to Suzhou from Shanghai by Beijing-Shanghai Railway Line,

203
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:07,120
and finally moved into Gu's Garden.

204
00:12:07,270 --> 00:12:07,870
By the way,

205
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,340
we seized the payroll book

206
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,620
of Suzhou Zone of the CBIS.

207
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,560
Sir, please take a look.

208
00:12:14,950 --> 00:12:16,120
Zhang Haimo

209
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:18,620
[Zhang Haimo, Member, 35 yuan, Salary]

210
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,920
receives an allowance of 35 yuan per month.

211
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:20,950
It is absolutely true.

212
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:30,840
How do you explain this?

213
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:33,100
Yeah.

214
00:12:33,950 --> 00:12:36,020
Explain to Mr. Kondo.

215
00:12:38,690 --> 00:12:40,190
[Zhang Haimo, 35 yuan, Salary]

216
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:51,590
Sir, please take a look.

217
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:54,520
It does have Haimo's name on it.

218
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:56,680
[Zhang Haimo, Member, 35 yuan, Salary]

219
00:12:55,090 --> 00:12:56,840
But Haimo's name is at the end.

220
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,910
It looks like it was added temporarily.

221
00:12:58,910 --> 00:13:00,070
Plus, the signature

222
00:13:00,180 --> 00:13:02,070
is not Zhang Haimo's handwriting at all.

223
00:13:02,070 --> 00:13:04,030
We seized this

224
00:13:04,030 --> 00:13:04,870
from Deyunzhi Travel Agency.

225
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:06,130
It should be credible.

226
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:11,650
Sir.

227
00:13:12,070 --> 00:13:13,810
After Haimo came to Suzhou,

228
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:15,970
except having been to Feng Garden Story-telling Theatre,

229
00:13:15,970 --> 00:13:18,050
she has been staying in Gu's Garden to take care of my father.

230
00:13:18,050 --> 00:13:19,510
My father also

231
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:21,950
handed over the title deed of Gu's Garden to her before he died.

232
00:13:21,950 --> 00:13:23,390
Haimo is simple-minded by nature.

233
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:26,230
She only performs storytelling accompanied by string instruments and knows nothing about politics.

234
00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:28,440
If she hasn't been made use of by someone with intentions,

235
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,990
there's absolutely no way she could get involved.

236
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:30,850
How about this?

237
00:13:31,690 --> 00:13:33,680
Zhang Haimo is currently in No. 90.

238
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:35,830
Let's put her to the torture.

239
00:13:36,020 --> 00:13:37,750
Then everything will be clear.

240
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:40,750
I can guarantee with my life

241
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:42,130
that she has nothing to do with the CBIS.

242
00:13:42,130 --> 00:13:44,230
I can also guarantee with my life

243
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:45,480
that Zhang Haimo

244
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:47,060
is a CBIS agent.

245
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:57,270
Since you're engaged and you love each other,

246
00:13:57,910 --> 00:13:59,910
why didn't you get married earlier?

247
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:05,460
My father passed away suddenly.

248
00:14:06,110 --> 00:14:08,310
It would be against the etiquette for me

249
00:14:08,370 --> 00:14:09,390
to get married during the mourning period.

250
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:11,430
The matter is urgent. Nowadays, during the war,

251
00:14:11,430 --> 00:14:14,690
you don't need to consider things like etiquette too much.

252
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:26,640
Sir.

253
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:28,030
What's up?

254
00:14:28,110 --> 00:14:30,270
Zhang Haimo has been tied up in the interrogation room.

255
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:31,870
Please let us know what to do.

256
00:14:32,210 --> 00:14:33,070
How about this?

257
00:14:33,490 --> 00:14:34,780
I'll interrogate her myself.

258
00:14:34,780 --> 00:14:35,660
Wait.

259
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:50,590
Gu,

260
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:55,130
do you dare to vouch for this woman?

261
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:58,640
I can vouch for her with my life.

262
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:01,240
Fine.

263
00:15:03,590 --> 00:15:04,610
Release her.

264
00:15:07,310 --> 00:15:07,700
No.

265
00:15:07,830 --> 00:15:09,030
I have a suggestion.

266
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:13,540
You two should get married.

267
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:17,540
It would also be a joyful event for No. 90.

268
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,610
That's it.

269
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:20,400
Zhou, allocate some budget

270
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:21,270
and make the wedding

271
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:22,310
a decent one.

272
00:15:27,570 --> 00:15:28,390
Sir, well…

273
00:15:28,430 --> 00:15:29,270
Go ahead.

274
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,370
Thank you, Sir.

275
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:39,740
Congratulations!

276
00:15:43,350 --> 00:15:43,950
Sir,

277
00:15:44,990 --> 00:15:46,390
I think Gu Yizhong not only…

278
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:48,250
Let's talk about it no more.

279
00:15:53,370 --> 00:15:54,210
Gu Yizhong.

280
00:15:55,470 --> 00:15:57,470
