[The Clouds Are Gone]

297
00:17:40,230 --> 00:17:41,370
[The Clouds Are Gone]

298
00:17:40,350 --> 00:17:41,070
Come here.

299
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:47,550
Get in the car first.

300
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:50,660
Don't worry about me.

301
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:52,070
It's okay.

302
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:05,100
Haimo is innocent.

303
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,730
In the current situation,

304
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,110
who dares to say

305
00:18:10,110 --> 00:18:11,440
that they are innocent?

306
00:18:15,590 --> 00:18:17,120
If you don't let go of Haimo,

307
00:18:18,550 --> 00:18:19,540
I'll report to Kondo

308
00:18:19,540 --> 00:18:21,070
that Ou Xinping was lurking

309
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,200
at your place.

310
00:18:23,150 --> 00:18:23,970
Also,

311
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:26,480
you released Jiang Boxian on purpose.

312
00:18:29,410 --> 00:18:30,380
Whatever.

313
00:18:30,410 --> 00:18:31,610
Tell Kondo.

314
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:33,060
Do you have evidence?

315
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:35,880
At the front gate of Willow Garden,

316
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:38,220
you helped Ou Xinping.

317
00:18:41,950 --> 00:18:43,680
You were really there that day.

318
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:48,680
When my father was alive, he liked collecting binoculars,

319
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,540
which were used in the German army

320
00:18:50,830 --> 00:18:52,150
and allowed one to see very far.

321
00:18:52,150 --> 00:18:53,070
So,

322
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:55,830
you killed the first-class shooter

323
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:57,270
of the Peace Army?

324
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,980
He killed too many people.

325
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,010
That was his retribution.

326
00:19:02,010 --> 00:19:03,080
This is good.

327
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:05,360
Retribution.

328
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:11,180
Gu Yizhong.

329
00:19:12,270 --> 00:19:13,640
Which one of us

330
