do you think

331
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,770
can avoid retribution?

332
00:19:26,330 --> 00:19:28,380
Don't underestimate Kondo.

333
00:19:29,390 --> 00:19:31,210
He asked you to marry Haimo

334
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:32,630
in the hope

335
00:19:32,650 --> 00:19:34,850
that you would leave the Communist Party.

336
00:19:34,850 --> 00:19:36,710
Just like some time ago he asked me

337
00:19:36,950 --> 00:19:39,150
to execute Ou Xinping personally.

338
00:19:39,950 --> 00:19:41,200
In No. 90,

339
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:43,660
if you want to live one more day,

340
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:46,270
you must learn

341
00:19:46,290 --> 00:19:48,150
to read the minds of the Japanese.

342
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:49,600
Otherwise,

343
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,920
you wouldn't even know how you died.

344
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:57,090
Those of us

345
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:59,050
who defected from the CBIS and NBIS

346
00:20:00,330 --> 00:20:02,460
can easily be trusted by the Japanese.

347
00:20:03,080 --> 00:20:06,680
But those of you who were from the Communist Party are different.

348
00:20:08,180 --> 00:20:09,610
The Communists

349
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:12,180
are firm in their belief.

350
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:15,060
If you really want to defect

351
00:20:15,250 --> 00:20:16,980
and be trusted by the Japanese,

352
00:20:17,820 --> 00:20:19,620
it will be much harder than we do.

353
00:20:20,610 --> 00:20:21,620
But luckily,

354
00:20:22,170 --> 00:20:23,420
for now,

355
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:26,880
Kondo still trusts him.

356
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:32,140
Congratulations,

357
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:33,590
Vice Director Gu.

358
00:20:34,760 --> 00:20:36,240
Hurry and take her back.

359
00:20:36,700 --> 00:20:39,230
She'll definitely have a nightmare tonight.

360
00:20:50,190 --> 00:20:58,890
[Ready for Battle]

361
00:21:05,170 --> 00:21:06,320
What happened?

362
