You looked gloomy all the way.

363
00:21:11,020 --> 00:21:12,540
Why did they release me?

364
00:21:13,820 --> 00:21:14,730
Gu Yizhong.

365
00:21:20,170 --> 00:21:22,030
I'm going out to meet someone now.

366
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:24,660
You're not allowed to go anywhere

367
00:21:25,390 --> 00:21:26,670
before I come back.

368
00:21:27,670 --> 00:21:28,690
Understand?

369
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,210
No.

370
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:33,260
But I won't go anywhere.

371
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:41,240
Besides letting you get married,

372
00:21:41,380 --> 00:21:42,710
what else did Kondo say?

373
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:44,990
That day, he dragged me to his private residence,

374
00:21:44,990 --> 00:21:48,000
saying that he wanted to found the Sino-Japanese Cultural Association

375
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:49,390
and appoint me as president

376
00:21:49,390 --> 00:21:50,590
to manㅁㅎㄷ the matter.

377
00:21:51,690 --> 00:21:52,690
He also said

378
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:55,260
that he couldn't trust Zhou Zhifei.

379
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:56,280
By the way,

380
00:21:56,620 --> 00:21:58,890
Zhou Zhifei called me Vice Director just now.

381
00:21:58,890 --> 00:21:59,850
That's strange.

382
00:21:59,990 --> 00:22:00,950
That matches up

383
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:04,190
with the intelligence that our undercover agent in No. 76 got.

384
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,790
Mr. Li just signed you on

385
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:07,250
as Vice Director of No. 90.

386
00:22:07,370 --> 00:22:09,570
I heard that the Japanese requested it.

387
00:22:14,370 --> 00:22:15,270
The Japanese are obviously trying

388
00:22:15,270 --> 00:22:16,300
to drag me into it.

389
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:19,960
Back then, they didn't let my father off.

390
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:22,230
Now they don't want to let me off either.

391
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:25,230
There are only two options.

392
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:26,070
Leave No. 90

393
00:22:26,310 --> 00:22:26,910
or

394
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:28,950
make use of the current situation

395
00:22:28,950 --> 00:22:30,110
and marry Haimo.

396
00:22:31,550 --> 00:22:32,350
Impossible.

397
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:34,230
I can't marry Haimo.

398
00:22:34,250 --> 00:22:34,870
Sir,

399
00:22:34,970 --> 00:22:36,660
I've already proposed to Xiao Ruotong.

400
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:38,020
And she accepted it.

401
00:22:38,150 --> 00:22:38,880
I endured humiliation

402
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,120
just for this day.

403
00:22:40,410 --> 00:22:42,540
I didn't ask you to really marry Haimo.

404
00:22:42,870 --> 00:22:44,330
It's just a fake marriage.

405
00:22:47,390 --> 00:22:48,320
What do you mean?

406
00:22:48,580 --> 00:22:50,120
In our undercover work,

407
00:22:50,210 --> 00:22:51,750
we often need to pretend to be a couple with someone

408
00:22:51,750 --> 00:22:52,710
and work together.

409
00:22:52,710 --> 00:22:54,630
It's called "setting a trap" in the party.

410
00:22:54,630 --> 00:22:55,630
I don't accept it.

411
00:22:56,560 --> 00:22:57,820
I don't want to do this.

412
00:22:58,800 --> 00:23:00,410
I have some bad news for you.

413
00:23:02,080 --> 00:23:02,860
Fu Gui

414
00:23:03,390 --> 00:23:04,590
sacrificed himself.

415
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:05,920
It happened just now.

416
00:23:06,430 --> 00:23:07,510
The agents of No. 90

417
00:23:07,540 --> 00:23:08,750
went to Dingjue Temple to arrest him.

418
00:23:08,750 --> 00:23:10,160
He would rather die than being arrested.

419
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,820
And he died with the enemies.

420
00:23:14,580 --> 00:23:15,450
Impossible.

421
00:23:15,470 --> 00:23:16,740
I contacted Xiao Ruotong a long time ago

422
00:23:16,740 --> 00:23:17,730
and let her tell him to leave Suzhou.

423
00:23:17,730 --> 00:23:19,640
Why was he still in Dingjue Temple?

424
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,240
It's impossible. I don't believe it.

425
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,500
He didn't want to leave

426
00:23:23,690 --> 00:23:25,150
because he didn't want to stand by

427
00:23:25,150 --> 00:23:26,480
and give up his hometown

428
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:28,590
to the Japanese.

429
00:23:29,130 --> 00:23:30,060
So he had to fight

430
00:23:30,150 --> 00:23:31,680
even if he would have to die.

431
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:38,290
How would this happen?

432
00:23:41,990 --> 00:23:42,550
Yizhong,

433
00:23:43,910 --> 00:23:45,310
I don't want to force you.

434
00:23:46,510 --> 00:23:48,970
Now, Kondo asked you to be the Vice Director.

435
00:23:49,470 --> 00:23:50,830
You'll be likely to have access

436
00:23:50,830 --> 00:23:52,910
to intelligence that is more of the core.

437
00:23:52,910 --> 00:23:54,440
It's a rare opportunity

438
00:23:54,470 --> 00:23:56,580
for us who do undercover work.

