00:24:20,940 --> 00:24:21,580
Father.

441
00:24:23,290 --> 00:24:24,350
What should I do?

442
00:24:45,020 --> 00:24:47,740
Young Master, I'm sorry.

443
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:51,360
When you read this letter,

444
00:24:52,420 --> 00:24:54,370
I'm already dead.

445
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,070
Please don't blame Miss Xiao.

446
00:24:57,420 --> 00:24:59,270
I decided not to leave.

