00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:01,980
As a soldier,

448
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:04,130
I should have died on the battlefield.

449
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:06,980
It's already a great shame to live a few more years.

450
00:25:09,090 --> 00:25:11,460
I had been following Division Commander closely

451
00:25:11,460 --> 00:25:12,870
