454
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:20,020
People from the family

455
00:25:20,020 --> 00:25:22,680
cannot disgrace the reputation of Gu's Garden.

456
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:27,830
I know that the meaning of the word "loyalty"

457
00:25:28,100 --> 00:25:29,700
weighs heavier than my life.

458
00:25:31,230 --> 00:25:32,550
Division Commander will see the day

459
00:25:32,550 --> 00:25:34,950
on which the Japanese get out of Suzhou.

460
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:37,600
Don't worry, Young Master.

461
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:41,160
I'll take good care of Division Commander over there.

462
00:25:42,970 --> 00:25:43,810
Fu Gui.

463
00:25:44,100 --> 00:25:45,110
Interrogate me?

464
00:25:45,730 --> 00:25:46,980
Cut the crap.

465
00:25:48,390 --> 00:25:50,580
Don't. Don't. Chinese don't beat Chinese.

