00:28:30,030 --> 00:28:30,910
Back then, Helv, King of Wu,

501
00:28:30,910 --> 00:28:32,750
sent Wu Zixu to build Helv City.

502
00:28:34,790 --> 00:28:36,810
According to the Spring and Autumn Annals of Wu and Yue,

503
00:28:36,810 --> 00:28:38,430
Zixu asked the physiognomist to taste the water

504
00:28:38,430 --> 00:28:39,980
and applied the principle of Modeling Heaven and Earth

505
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:41,310
to build the great city.

506
00:28:43,270 --> 00:28:45,060
How big was Helv City?

507
00:28:46,150 --> 00:28:47,580
According to The Glory of Yue,

508
00:28:47,580 --> 00:28:50,560
it was 47 li, 210 bu, and two chi

509
00:28:50,950 --> 00:28:52,630
in perimeter.

510
00:28:53,470 --> 00:28:55,120
There were eight land city gates

511
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:56,580
