512
00:28:56,580 --> 00:28:58,640
It took three years to build the city.

513
00:29:01,390 --> 00:29:02,590
The Helv City

514
00:29:03,230 --> 00:29:05,030
is the current Suzhou City.

515
00:29:06,960 --> 00:29:08,930
When the ground was broken to build the city,

516
00:29:08,930 --> 00:29:11,450
it was the sixth year of King Jing of Zhou's reign.

517
00:29:11,450 --> 00:29:14,080
That is, 514 BC.

518
00:29:15,820 --> 00:29:17,170
It was a long time ago.

519
00:29:19,510 --> 00:29:20,820
It's been 2,500 years.

520
00:29:23,870 --> 00:29:26,800
I didn't realize Suzhou has so many years of history.

521
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:31,060
Back then, Japanese architect Sekino Tadashi said

522
00:29:32,290 --> 00:29:34,910
that there was no ancient architecture in China,

523
00:29:34,910 --> 00:29:38,230
and the earliest Tang Dynasty architecture was in Kyoto, Japan.

524
00:29:38,230 --> 00:29:39,650
Mr. Liang Sicheng and Miss Lin Huiyin

525
00:29:39,650 --> 00:29:40,780
were not convinced.

526
00:29:41,610 --> 00:29:42,940
It took them seven years

527
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:46,600
to finally find Tang Dynasty architecture

528
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:48,520
in Foguang Temple of Mount Wutai.

529
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,860
In 1936,

530
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:54,040
Mr. Liang specially wrote a letter to me,

531
00:29:54,470 --> 00:29:55,670
asking me to measure

532
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:58,480
and protect the ancient Suzhou architecture.

533
00:29:59,310 --> 00:30:01,450
I wanted to make my humble effort.

534
00:30:02,010 --> 00:30:03,300
But once the war began,

535
00:30:04,910 --> 00:30:06,570
even people are all like ants,

536
00:30:08,290 --> 00:30:09,890
let alone the architecture.

537
00:30:11,630 --> 00:30:12,640
Mr. Gu,

538
00:30:13,550 --> 00:30:15,010
I don't really understand

539
00:30:16,650 --> 00:30:17,850
what you said.

540
00:30:18,530 --> 00:30:19,700
But I know

541
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,590
you're a decent man

542
00:30:22,360 --> 00:30:23,510
like Uncle Gu.

543
00:30:24,070 --> 00:30:25,760
You're the ones

544
00:30:26,280 --> 00:30:28,080
who really know and love Suzhou.

545
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:34,890
We can't allow the bandits to trample on Suzhou city,

546
00:30:35,410 --> 00:30:37,900
which has a history of 2,500 years.

547
00:30:38,980 --> 00:30:41,110
I know that Uncle Gu hasn't been buried

548
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:44,040
because he's waiting for the day

549
00:30:44,040 --> 00:30:45,840
on which the Japanese

550
00:30:45,870 --> 00:30:46,870
get out of Suzhou.

551
00:30:57,420 --> 00:30:58,130
Haimo.

552
00:31:00,350 --> 00:31:02,040
I have to stay in No. 90.

553
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:04,590
I need to cut off all my connections with the past.

554
00:31:04,590 --> 00:31:06,990
In order to continue to gain Kondo's trust,

555
00:31:08,320 --> 00:31:10,780
I have to make my current identity authentic

556
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:13,330
so that I can do what I should do better.

557
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,920
Our country is on the brink of survival.

558
00:31:18,610 --> 00:31:21,140
We must fight without concern for ourselves.

559
00:31:25,430 --> 00:31:26,410
Mr. Gu,

560
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:29,640
if you have anything to say,

561
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:32,140
just say it.

562
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:35,100
I'll do whatever you say.

563
00:31:51,270 --> 00:31:52,070
Haimo,

564
00:31:56,470 --> 00:31:57,640
will you marry me?

565
00:32:44,620 --> 00:32:45,310
Junxia.

566
00:32:46,660 --> 00:32:47,330
Look.

567
00:32:47,870 --> 00:32:50,000
The color of the yarn is nice, isn't it?

568
00:32:50,600 --> 00:32:51,540
Yes.

569
00:32:52,280 --> 00:32:53,340
It's getting cold.

570
00:32:53,740 --> 00:32:55,740
I'm going to knit a new scarf for Yizhong.

571
00:32:55,740 --> 00:32:56,740
He will need it.

572
00:32:56,950 --> 00:32:57,560
Ruotong.

573
00:33:00,860 --> 00:33:01,660
What's wrong?

574
00:33:05,510 --> 00:33:07,070
Why do you look so serious?

575
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:09,520
Is the ship not able to leave?

576
00:33:09,770 --> 00:33:11,170
We're not able to go back?

577
00:33:11,390 --> 00:33:12,530
The ship can leave.

578
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,190
But he just

579
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:16,150
can't leave with us for now.

580
00:33:16,940 --> 00:33:17,710
Why?

581
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:20,220
I don't know the specific reason either.

582
00:33:21,660 --> 00:33:23,590
Is there something holding him up?

583
00:33:24,350 --> 00:33:26,390
Did something happen at the agent station?

584
00:33:26,390 --> 00:33:27,390
Did they suspect him?

585
00:33:27,390 --> 00:33:28,070
Is he in danger?

586
00:33:28,070 --> 00:33:29,350
No. Not at all.

587
00:33:29,980 --> 00:33:31,840
He suddenly decided not to leave.

588
00:33:32,790 --> 00:33:34,430
There must be a reason.

589
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:36,080
I'll go ask him.

590
00:33:36,110 --> 00:33:36,670
No, you can't go.

591
00:33:36,670 --> 00:33:37,390
Why?

592
00:33:40,110 --> 00:33:40,910
Ruotong.

593
00:33:44,510 --> 00:33:45,460
Forget him.

594
00:33:47,010 --> 00:33:47,910
Why?

595
00:33:47,940 --> 00:33:49,670
Because he's getting married.

596
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:51,140
Nonsense!

597
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:53,680
Why didn't I know that he…

598
00:33:54,010 --> 00:33:55,400
How can he get married?

599
00:33:55,430 --> 00:33:56,570
Who would he marry without me?

600
00:33:56,570 --> 00:33:57,230
Haimo.

601
00:34:01,290 --> 00:34:07,240
[Pavilion of Pleasantness]

602
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:11,510
You should tell her face to face.

603
00:34:16,290 --> 00:34:17,860
I'll regret it if I do so.

604
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:21,520
I don't have the courage to stand in front of her

605
00:34:22,080 --> 00:34:24,139
or say those words.

606
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:27,560
I let her down.

607
00:34:30,610 --> 00:34:32,550
The wedding will be held the day after tomorrow.

608
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:34,010
A Western-style wedding.

609
00:34:34,469 --> 00:34:36,070
It will be held in the church.

610
00:35:14,090 --> 00:35:16,360
[Pavilion of Pleasantness]

611
00:35:15,310 --> 00:35:16,770
I know what you want to say.

612
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:20,780
You have only Miss Xiao

613
00:35:21,530 --> 00:35:22,660
in your heart.

614
00:35:24,110 --> 00:35:25,370
No one can replace her.

615
00:35:28,200 --> 00:35:30,760
I only have one wish now.

616
00:35:31,610 --> 00:35:33,810
That is to avenge the deaths of Uncle Gu,

617
00:35:33,910 --> 00:35:34,970
my cousin-in-law,

618
00:35:35,950 --> 00:35:37,540
and Butler Fu.

619
00:35:38,660 --> 00:35:40,390
I'm a woman without talent.

620
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:44,740
If I can set a trap with you by pretending to be a couple,

621
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:45,870
I'm willing to do so.

622
00:35:48,010 --> 00:35:48,870
Don't worry.

623
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:52,130
I can play the role of the wife well.

624
00:35:53,100 --> 00:35:53,960
I'm just afraid

625
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:58,100
that you can't play the role of the husband well.

626
00:36:56,220 --> 00:36:59,260
[Your whole family is invited. Gu Yizhong, Zhang Haimo. Bow]

627
00:37:03,350 --> 00:37:04,150
What's wrong?

628
00:37:06,110 --> 00:37:07,870
Gu Yizhong is getting married.

629
00:37:26,850 --> 00:37:27,510
Sir.

630
00:37:28,690 --> 00:37:29,310
Please.

631
00:37:48,770 --> 00:37:50,240
[Your whole family is invited. Gu Yizhong, Zhang Haimo. Bow]

632
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:52,030
This is the first time

633
00:37:52,030 --> 00:37:54,430
I received a wedding invitation from Chinese people.

634
00:37:54,430 --> 00:37:57,350
But is it appropriate for me to attend it?

635
00:37:58,670 --> 00:37:59,390
Sir.

636
00:37:59,410 --> 00:38:00,270
No matter what,

637
00:38:01,030 --> 00:38:02,090
congratulations.

638
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:05,940
Get ready.

639
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:11,250
This is some premium fabric

640
00:38:12,590 --> 00:38:13,880
for Lady Haimo.

641
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:16,040
Make a dress from the fabric.

642
00:38:16,940 --> 00:38:17,580
Thank you.

643
00:38:19,110 --> 00:38:20,630
Zhang Haimo.

644
00:38:21,290 --> 00:38:22,650
Who is this lady?

645
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:25,230
Didn't you say

646
00:38:25,230 --> 00:38:26,060
he's dating a female Communist?

647
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:27,590
Not that female Communist.

648
00:38:28,310 --> 00:38:29,690
This is a fake.

649
00:38:29,950 --> 00:38:32,090
Ji, we need to give some presents.

650
00:38:32,810 --> 00:38:33,860
I'm not going,

651
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:35,640
in case it's a trap.

652
00:38:35,980 --> 00:38:37,090
If we all go,

653
00:38:37,430 --> 00:38:38,630
we will all be caught.

654
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,770
Even if we don't go,

655
00:38:40,950 --> 00:38:42,750
we need to send the presents too.

656
00:38:42,790 --> 00:38:43,650
How about this?

657
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:45,790
Send him the mirror

658
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:47,230
with the mandarin ducks playing in the water

659
00:38:47,230 --> 00:38:48,430
that we got last year,

660
00:38:49,230 --> 00:38:52,250
plus the dragon and phoenix gold bracelet in our house.

661
00:38:52,250 --> 00:38:53,050
Are you crazy?

662
00:38:53,740 --> 00:38:55,710
You give your enemy such a big gift?

663
00:38:55,740 --> 00:38:58,400
I don't care whether his marriage is real or not.

664
00:38:58,560 --> 00:39:00,640
Our presents have to be real.

665
00:39:01,750 --> 00:39:02,980
W-What?

666
00:39:03,270 --> 00:39:04,050
What? Marriage…

667
00:39:04,050 --> 00:39:05,490
A marriage can be fake?

668
00:39:05,900 --> 00:39:06,760
You never know.

669
00:39:08,820 --> 00:39:09,430
Now, Gu Yizhong

670
00:39:09,430 --> 00:39:11,070
is the Vice Director of No. 90

671
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,930
and Kondo's favorite person.

672
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:15,430
As the saying goes,

673
00:39:15,540 --> 00:39:17,000
the more friends you have,

674
00:39:17,110 --> 00:39:18,970
the more options you have in life.

675
00:39:20,430 --> 00:39:21,580
Hurry up and go prepare.

676
00:39:21,580 --> 00:39:24,240
I feel guilty about sending that many presents.

677
00:40:19,150 --> 00:40:20,320
Miss Zhang Haimo.

678
00:40:21,040 --> 00:40:23,290
Will you take Mr. Gu Yizhong

679
00:40:23,310 --> 00:40:24,730
to be your husband?

680
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:27,550
Whether in sickness or in health

681
00:40:27,870 --> 00:40:29,770
or for any other reason,

682
00:40:30,110 --> 00:40:32,500
will you love him, take care of him,

683
00:40:32,780 --> 00:40:35,320
respect him, accept him,

684
00:40:35,660 --> 00:40:38,630
and always be loyal to him

685
00:40:39,310 --> 00:40:41,150
until the end of your life?

686
00:40:43,270 --> 00:40:44,110
Yes, I will.

687
00:40:45,140 --> 00:40:46,540
Mr. Gu Yizhong.

688
00:40:46,950 --> 00:40:49,450
Will you take Miss Zhang Haimo

689
00:40:49,550 --> 00:40:50,950
to be your wife?

690
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:53,610
Whether in sickness or in health

691
00:40:53,640 --> 00:40:55,200
or for any other reason,

692
00:40:55,640 --> 00:40:58,060
will you love her, take care of her,

693
00:40:58,480 --> 00:41:00,440
respect her, accept her,

694
00:40:58,660 --> 00:41:01,250
[Dear Xiao Ruotong]

695
00:41:01,020 --> 00:41:03,110
and always be loyal to her

696
00:41:03,640 --> 00:41:05,550
until the end of your life?

697
00:41:08,710 --> 00:41:10,020
Mr. Gu Yizhong.

698
00:41:26,390 --> 00:41:27,230
Yes, I will.

699
00:41:29,910 --> 00:41:31,900
Now, you can exchange rings.

700
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:56,740
Wish you love each other

701
00:41:56,770 --> 00:41:57,930
for the rest of your lives.

702
00:41:57,930 --> 00:41:59,860
The bridegroom can kiss the bride.

703
00:42:03,990 --> 00:42:05,220
Kiss her!

704
00:42:06,120 --> 00:42:07,300
Kiss her!
